{"tid":2178397,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【全民檢測】發通告籲全體員工參與　聖公會福利協會：檢測可作工時計算","createTime":"2020-08-28T10:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T11:06:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4db396e1c8bd9988342de8b170620d2174797192","tid":2178397,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:56:50.000Z","msg":"全民檢測計劃 9 月 1 日開始，政府今日（28 日）公布 141 間採集樣本中心，遍及全港 18 區。建制派發聲表示全力支持計劃，又指將參與 9 月 1 日於立法會大樓的檢測；教育局局長楊潤雄則發文表示「希望」校長老師積極參與全民檢測，詳見相關報道。社福機構聖公會福利協會本周一亦發通告，呼籲全體員工參與全民檢測，對於員工政治上的顧慮及抗疫疲勞，協會促員工「以大局為重，共同抗疫」；又指為鼓勵員工參與，檢測可當作工時計算。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/全民檢測-發通告籲全體員工參與-聖公會福利協會-檢測可作工時計算/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E7%99%BC%E9%80%9A%E5%91%8A%E7%B1%B2%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%94%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87-%E8%81%96%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%A9%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83-%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E5%8F%AF%E4%BD%9C%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%82%E8%A8%88%E7%AE%97%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=ecde3b15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E7%99%BC%E9%80%9A%E5%91%8A%E7%B1%B2%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%94%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87-%E8%81%96%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%A9%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83-%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E5%8F%AF%E4%BD%9C%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%82%E8%A8%88%E7%AE%97%2F&h=6b3e4fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/全民檢測-發通告籲全體員工參與-聖公會福利協會-檢測可作工時計算/</a>"},{"pid":"ae09445b66d2eca7ec08ac224b48271f9bbd0b8a","tid":2178397,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:59:27.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：教育界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbd164c7aaa765a9bcb8e4420e7464b80129fb0","tid":2178397,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":